{
  "info": {
    "name": "PROGRESS-TRACKING",
    "description": "Media Progress + Category Progress + Journey Progress + Session Progress",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl",    "value": "https://your-tunnel.trycloudflare.com/api", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "userToken",  "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "mediaId",    "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "categoryId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "journeyId",  "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "📹 Media Progress",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Update Media Progress",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{userToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"watchedSeconds\": 120,\n  \"totalSeconds\": 300\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/progress/media/{{mediaId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["progress", "media", "{{mediaId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Flutter video player থেকে প্রতি 10-15 সেকেন্ডে call করুন।\n\nwatchedSeconds = user কতক্ষণ দেখেছে\ntotalSeconds   = ভিডিওর মোট দৈর্ঘ্য\n\nBackend calculate করে:\n  percentage  = (120 / 300) * 100 = 40%\n  isCompleted = percentage >= 80"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "📂 Category Progress",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Category Progress",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{userToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/progress/category/{{categoryId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["progress", "category", "{{categoryId}}"]
            },
            "description": "একটি category তে user কতটুকু complete করেছে।\n\nExample response:\n{\n  \"categoryProgress\": 60,\n  \"totalMedia\": 5,\n  \"completedMedia\": 3,\n  \"mediaList\": [...]\n}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🗺️ Journey Progress (Media-based)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Journey Progress",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{userToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/progress/journey/{{journeyId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["progress", "journey", "{{journeyId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Journey-এর সব category মিলিয়ে মোট progress।\n\nExample response:\n{\n  \"journeyProgress\": 45,\n  \"totalCategories\": 12,\n  \"completedCategories\": 5,\n  \"categories\": [...]\n}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🧠 Session Progress (EMDR Journey)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Update Session Progress",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const r = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (r.success) {",
                  "  console.log('Progress updated:', r.data.totalCompledSession);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{userToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"journeyId\": \"{{journeyId}}\",\n  \"totalSession\": 10,\n  \"compledSession\": 6\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/session-progress/update",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["session-progress", "update"]
            },
            "description": "একটি Journey-এর EMDR session progress update করুন।\n\nField গুলো:\n  journeyId      — Journey এর ObjectId\n  totalSession   — Journey তে মোট কতটি session আছে\n  compledSession — User কতটি session complete করেছে\n\nBackend calculate করে:\n  progressPercentage = Math.round((compledSession / totalSession) * 100) + '%'\n\nExample: totalSession=10, compledSession=6 → \"60%\"\n\nNote: compledSession > totalSession হলে validation error আসবে।\n\nExample response:\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"totalCompledSession\": \"60%\",\n    \"details\": {\n      \"totalSessions\": 10,\n      \"completedSessions\": 6\n    }\n  }\n}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Session Progress",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{userToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/session-progress/{{journeyId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["session-progress", "{{journeyId}}"]
            },
            "description": "একটি Journey-এ user এর EMDR session progress দেখুন।\n\nPath param:\n  journeyId — Journey এর ObjectId\n\nProgress না থাকলে 0% return করে (error দেয় না)।\n\nExample response (progress আছে):\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"totalCompledSession\": \"60%\",\n    \"details\": {\n      \"totalSessions\": 10,\n      \"completedSessions\": 6\n    }\n  }\n}\n\nExample response (progress নেই):\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"totalCompledSession\": \"0%\",\n    \"details\": {\n      \"totalSessions\": 0,\n      \"completedSessions\": 0\n    }\n  }\n}"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🛠️ Setup — Create Journey",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Journey",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const r = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (r.success) pm.collectionVariables.set('journeyId', r.data._id);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{userToken}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type",  "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"journeyName\": \"Healing Journey\",\n  \"description\": \"A 12-week EMDR healing program\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/journeys",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["journeys"]
            },
            "description": "Test এর জন্য একটি Journey তৈরি করুন।\nTest script স্বয়ংক্রিয়ভাবে journeyId variable সেট করে দেবে।"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
